'''Apple A8'''是[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]設計的第二代[[64位元|64位元]][[系統單晶片|系統單晶片]]（SoC）。在2014年9月9日發佈，用於[[iPhone_6|iPhone 6]]、[[iPhone_6_Plus|iPhone 6 Plus]]、[[iPad_mini_4|iPad mini 4]]、[[iPod_touch_6|iPod touch 6]]、[[Apple_TV|Apple TV]]和[[HomePod|HomePod]]。<ref name="Apple iPhone 6 PR">{{cite press release |url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2014/09/09Apple-Announces-iPhone-6-iPhone-6-Plus-The-Biggest-Advancements-in-iPhone-History.html |title=Apple Announces iPhone 6 & iPhone 6 Plus—The Biggest Advancements in iPhone History |publisher=Apple |date=2014-09-09 |accessdate=2014-09-09 |archive-date=2014-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140909213704/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2014/09/09Apple-Announces-iPhone-6-iPhone-6-Plus-The-Biggest-Advancements-in-iPhone-History.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
蘋果公司宣稱它比上代[[Apple_A7|Apple A7]]在[[CPU|CPU]]效能高25%，繪圖效能高50%，能源效益高50%。<ref name="Verge A8">{{cite news |last=Savov |first=Vlad |title=iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus have a new faster A8 processor |url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/9/9/6127111/iphone-6-and-iphone-6-plus-have-a-new-faster-a8-processor |work=The Verge |publisher=Vox Media |date=2014-09-09 |accessdate=2014-09-09 |archive-date=2014-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910225625/http://www.theverge.com/2014/9/9/6127111/iphone-6-and-iphone-6-plus-have-a-new-faster-a8-processor |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 技術 ==
CPU部份為自家定制的「改良版Cyclone」，上代A7則是「Cyclone」，維持雙核心設計，L1[[CPU快取|快取]]為64KB指令+64KB數據，L2為1MB，L3則為4MB。GPU則採用[[Imagination_Technologies|Imagination Technologies]]的[[PowerVR|PowerVR]] GX6450，核心數目依然為4個，依蘋果公司的宣稱，比上代繪圖效能高50%。<ref name="anandtech analyzing">{{cite news|author=Ryan Smith|title=Analyzing Apple’s A8 SoC: PowerVR GX6650 & More|url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/8514/analyzing-apples-a8-soc-gx6650-more|accessdate=2014-09-21|newspaper=Anandtech|date=September 10, 2014 5:00 AM EST|archive-date=2014-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921054419/http://www.anandtech.com/show/8514/analyzing-apples-a8-soc-gx6650-more|dead-url=no}}</ref>值得一提的是蘋果公司也持有Imagination Technologies公司9.5%股權。

Apple A8採用[[台灣積體電路製造公司|台灣積體電路製造公司]]20nm製程生產<ref name="AnandTech-Apple-Announces-A8">{{cite web |last=Smith |first=Ryan |url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/8504/apple-announces-a8-soc |title=Apple Announces A8 SoC |publisher=AnandTech |date=2014-09-09 |accessdate=2014-09-09 |archive-date=2014-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910200128/http://www.anandtech.com/show/8504/apple-announces-a8-soc |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Chipworks-iPhone6">{{cite web|url=http://www.chipworks.com/en/technical-competitive-analysis/resources/blog/inside-the-iphone-6-and-iphone-6-plus/|title=Inside the iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus|publisher=Chipworks|date=2014-09-19|accessdate=2014-09-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924015413/http://www.chipworks.com/en/technical-competitive-analysis/resources/blog/inside-the-iphone-6-and-iphone-6-plus/|archivedate=2014-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，不再由[[三星電子|三星]]代工。

它包含20億個[[電晶體|電晶體]]，大約是Apple A7的兩倍，晶粒大小卻減少13%，由102mm<sup>2</sup>減至89mm<sup>2</sup>（沒有採用新架構，只是電晶體排得密）。<ref name="extremetech" />1GB LP[[DDR3|DDR3]]記憶體亦一同封裝在SoC。<ref name="iiPhone6PlusTeardown" />iPhone 6採用的LPDDR3記憶體是由[[Hynix|SK Hynix]]生產，iPhone 6 Plus的記憶體則由[[Elpida|Elpida]]生產。<ref>{{cite news|title=逐漸擺脫 Samsung，Apple A8 SoC 處理器由台灣 TSMC 代工|url=http://chinese.vr-zone.com/128303/apple-a8-soc-cpu-made-by-taiwan-tsmc-confirm-by-chipworks-09212014/|accessdate=2014-09-21|newspaper=vr-zone|date=2014-09-21|archive-date=2014-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921195643/http://chinese.vr-zone.com/128303/apple-a8-soc-cpu-made-by-taiwan-tsmc-confirm-by-chipworks-09212014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Geekbench[[基準測試|基準測試]]顯示處理器為雙核心，頻率1.38GHz，符合蘋果公司的宣稱（比上代快25%）。<ref name="Geekbench"/>

